515
00:37:47,066 --> 00:37:51,066
I know I'm in a similar situation...

516
00:37:57,066 --> 00:38:00,066
What... did you do?

517
00:38:03,066 --> 00:38:11,066
Yesterday, I was grabbed by my hair and dragged around.

518
00:38:11,066 --> 00:38:14,066
``It's payday for your part-time job. Give me the money.''

519
00:38:17,066 --> 00:38:20,066
I don't want to go home anymore.

520
00:38:24,066 --> 00:38:29,066
But I have to go home and make some food...

521
00:38:29,066 --> 00:38:32,066
(whimper)

522
00:38:32,066 --> 00:38:43,066
♬〜

523
00:38:43,066 --> 00:38:47,066
I'll... finish it.

524
00:38:49,066 --> 00:38:54,066
(Fukazawa's voice) I will end my son's life→

525
00:38:54,066 --> 00:39:00,066
The money he took will be used to pay off his daughter's debts.

526
00:39:00,066 --> 00:39:02,066
Let's do that...

527
00:39:03,066 --> 00:39:08,066
I refused, saying I didn't want my son to die.

528
00:39:08,066 --> 00:39:11,066
But that night →

529
00:39:11,066 --> 00:39:15,066
When my son asked me for money and I refused...

530
00:39:17,066 --> 00:39:21,066
(Yurie's voice) I was strangled and lost consciousness...

531
00:39:22,066 --> 00:39:25,066
(Yurie's voice) I...

532
00:39:26,066 --> 00:39:29,066
My heart died at that moment.

533
00:39:32,066 --> 00:39:35,066
I said please do that.

534
00:39:37,066 --> 00:39:40,066
It was mutually agreed upon.

535
00:39:42,066 --> 00:39:45,066
That's what we both wanted to do...

536
00:39:46,066 --> 00:39:51,066
My family and this family →

537
00:39:51,066 --> 00:39:55,066
There was no way to solve it.

538
00:39:55,066 --> 00:40:02,066
♬〜

539
00:40:02,066 --> 00:40:04,066
What money did you take?

540
00:40:05,066 --> 00:40:11,066
to my account. Haven't used it for repayment yet.

541
00:40:15,066 --> 00:40:22,066
Mr. Fukazawa is suspected of robbery and murder, and Mr. Sasano is suspected of concealing the perpetrator...→

542
00:40:22,066 --> 00:40:24,066
I will arrest you.

543
00:40:24,066 --> 00:40:31,066
♬〜

544
00:40:31,066 --> 00:40:33,066
Please wait!

545
00:40:35,066 --> 00:40:38,066
Don't the police just make arrests?

546
00:40:38,066 --> 00:40:41,066
Is that why you work as a detective?

547
00:40:42,066 --> 00:40:47,066
We...we, the police, could have done something earlier...

548
00:40:47,066 --> 00:40:51,066
I wish I could help you sooner...

549
00:40:51,066 --> 00:40:56,066
I was able to listen to the voices of people who were suffering and empathize with them.

550
00:41:05,066 --> 00:41:08,066
Keep that feeling in your heart.

551
00:41:08,066 --> 00:41:10,066
(sound of handcuffs)

552
00:41:10,066 --> 00:41:22,066
♬〜

553
00:41:22,066 --> 00:41:25,066
(Mio) Sleeping comfortably...

554
00:41:27,066 --> 00:41:32,066
Probably because it freed me from suffering.

555
00:41:32,066 --> 00:41:39,066
Regarding my daughter... could you please shut up?

556
00:41:41,066 --> 00:41:47,066
If possible, I would like to work at Ichiboshi for a little longer.

557
00:41:51,066 --> 00:41:56,066
Knowing that doesn't change your perspective.

558
00:41:57,066 --> 00:42:01,066
Mr. Kuro is an excellent detective.

559
00:42:01,066 --> 00:42:05,066
A must-have for the Mobile Investigation Division.

560
00:42:05,066 --> 00:42:32,066
♬〜

561
00:42:32,066 --> 00:42:34,066
Where are you taking me?

562
00:42:34,066 --> 00:42:38,066
Let's watch the sunrise, Momoko-san. Huh...?

563
00:42:40,066 --> 00:42:44,066
Look, the sky is getting brighter...

564
00:42:44,066 --> 00:42:46,066
Huh?

565
00:42:48,066 --> 00:42:53,066
Even though it's bright, I can't see the sun. why?

566
00:42:53,066 --> 00:42:56,066
Well... →

567
00:42:56,066 --> 00:42:59,066
This is the west, right?

568
00:42:59,066 --> 00:43:01,066
yes.

569
00:43:06,066 --> 00:43:08,066
When does the sun rise?

570
00:43:09,066 --> 00:43:11,066
East... right?

571
00:43:11,066 --> 00:43:14,066
Then there's no way you can see the sun!

572
00:43:15,066 --> 00:43:17,066
Ah, I see.

573
00:43:17,066 --> 00:43:21,066
Is that so? Wow... I did it again.

574
00:43:21,066 --> 00:43:37,066
♬〜

575
00:43:37,066 --> 00:43:41,066
♬〜

576
00:43:41,066 --> 00:43:45,066
Thank you for your hard work. Please excuse me in advance.

577
00:43:45,066 --> 00:43:47,066
Yes, thank you for your hard work. (Mio) Thank you for your hard work.

578
00:44:03,066 --> 00:44:08,066
Regarding Manager Akase, there has been no suspicious behavior so far...

579
00:44:09,066 --> 00:44:13,066
We will continue to monitor.

580
00:44:17,066 --> 00:44:21,066
(Sound of keyboard hitting)

581
00:44:21,066 --> 00:44:30,066
♬〜
